OL,6,FA criminal investigation into a string
OL,7,Fof accusations of rape and sexual
OL,8,Fassault against Mohamed Al Fayed has
OL,9,Fwidened further, as ITV News reporter
OL,10,FMartha Fairlie reports
OL,12,FForty new allegations, including rape
OL,13,Fand sexual assault, relating to
OL,14,FMohamed Al Fayed and others are being
OL,15,Finvestigated by the Metropolitan
OL,16,FPolice.
OL,18,FThe Met say the claims relate to 40
OL,19,Falleged victims include allegations of
OL,20,Fsexual assault and rape between 1979
OL,21,Fand 2013.
