OL,3,CForty new allegations relating to Al
OL,4,CFayed being investigated
OL,6,FThese are in addition to the 21
OL,7,Fallegations relating to the former
OL,8,FHarrods' boss, who died last year aged
OL,9,F94, which the force knew about prior
OL,10,Fto the broadcast of a BBC documentary
OL,11,Flast month.
OL,13,FIn a statement on Friday, Commander
OL,14,FStephen Clayman said: "Since the
OL,15,Fbroadcast of the documentary and our
OL,16,Frecent appeal, detectives have
OL,17,Freceived numerous pieces of
OL,18,Finformation, predominantly relating to
OL,19,Fthe activities of Mohamed Al Fayed but
OL,20,Fsome relating to the actions of others.
