OL,3,CForty new allegations relating to Al
OL,4,CFayed being investigated
OL,6,FMr Clayman added: "While the majority
OL,7,Fof information we have received
OL,8,Frelates to Al Fayed's ownership of
OL,9,FHarrods, we are contacting
OL,10,Frepresentatives of other organisations
OL,11,Flinked to Al Fayed to ensure anyone
OL,12,Faffected is identified and has the
OL,13,Fopportunity to speak with us."
OL,15,FLast month, barristers representing
OL,16,Falleged victims of Al Fayed said they
OL,17,Fare now in touch with 60 people who
OL,18,Fhave said the former Harrods owner
OL,19,Fabused them.
