OL,3,CForty new allegations relating to Al
OL,4,CFayed being investigated
OL,6,FHarrods have launched an investigation
OL,7,Finto whether anyone currently working
OL,8,Ffor the luxury store had any
OL,9,Finvolvement in Al Fayed's alleged
OL,10,Fabuse.
OL,12,FThe current boss of Harrods, who also
OL,13,Fworked for Mohamed Al Fayed, has
OL,14,Fpreviously said the business "failed"
OL,15,Fits staff, but denied any knowledge of
OL,16,Fsexual misconduct allegations against
OL,17,Fthe former owner.
