OL,3,CForty new allegations relating to Al
OL,4,CFayed being investigated
OL,6,F"I feel it is important to make it
OL,7,Fclear that I was not aware of his
OL,8,Fcriminality and abuse," Harrods
OL,9,FManaging Director Michael Ward said in
OL,10,Fa statement released in September.
OL,12,FHe is stepping aside from charity
OL,13,Ftrusteeships while a review is
OL,14,Funderway.
OL,16,FMr Ward has been at Harrods since 2006
OL,17,Fand worked for Fayed until the change
OL,18,Fof ownership in 2010.
